---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Holiday Ornament Pottery Painting"
  description="Create custom holiday ornaments for your tree in Centerville, TN. Handmade treasures become family traditions!"
  price="$12-18"
  duration="1-1.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="custom ornaments, holiday ornaments, handmade Christmas, pottery ornaments, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Holiday Ornament Pottery Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Create beautiful, personalized holiday ornaments at Made @ The Local Pottery and Candle Studio that will become treasured family heirlooms. Paint custom ornaments that reflect your family's style and personality.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Select from our collection of quality ceramic ornament shapes—balls, bells, stars, snowflakes, angels, and more. Paint them with designs that represent your family or create personalized ornaments with names, dates, or special memories. Professional ceramic paints ensure your designs are vibrant and long-lasting. After painting, we professionally glaze and kiln-fire each ornament so it becomes a durable heirloom. You'll have beautiful, one-of-a-kind ornaments for your tree that grow more meaningful each year.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Selection of ceramic ornament shapes</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints and colors</li>
      <li>Fine brushes for ornament painting</li>
      <li>Expert guidance on designs</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Ready-to-hang finished ornaments</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Creating family holiday traditions</li>
      <li>Personalized ornaments with names and dates</li>
      <li>Handmade Christmas gifts</li>
      <li>Building ornament collections</li>
      <li>Family holiday activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your ornament shape (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Design your custom ornament (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your design with guidance (40-50 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final details and hanging loop (5 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $12-18 per ornament<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1-1.5 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Create your custom ornaments!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"We paint a new ornament every year with our kids' names and the date. They'll treasure these forever!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Mary & James</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made custom ornaments for all my nieces and nephews. Such a special, personalized gift!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Aunt Susan</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Started this tradition 3 years ago. Every December we paint new family ornaments. Best tradition ever!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>The Rodriguez Family</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Seasonal Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Paint seasonal designs for holidays and celebrations.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/seasonal-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint Your Own Pottery Session</h3>
        <p>Choose from pre-made pottery pieces and paint them your way.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/paint-your-own-pottery-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Figurine Painting Workshop</h3>
        <p>Paint decorative ceramic figurines.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/figurine-painting-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
